com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl
Class AtomImpl<T extends Atom>

java.lang.Object
  com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl.AtomImpl<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Atom<T>, Buildable, Taggable, Versionable<T>, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Feature, FeatureList, MoleculeImpl, Tag
public abstract class AtomImpl<T extends Atom>
extends Object
implements Atom<T>

Implements core functionality that is shared by all classes that require tags. Deriving Feature and FeatureSet from one base class facilitates code re-use for interface implementations that are shared by those classes.
